description: You need lunch. We have curry. Come seek our truck!Established in 2006, Souvaly Thai Cuisine is located in West Oahu in the Pearl City Business Plaza, 803 Kamehameha Hwy. and is considered one of the finest Thai dining restaurants in Hawaii. It strives to deliver exceptionally tasty Asian specialties that even the most demanding of patrons can rely on its Thai authenticity.
name: Souvaly Thai
